    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p>Initiative details can be found here: <a href="https://jira.safeway.com/browse/ACIP-536162*" class="external-link" rel="nofollow">https://jira.safeway.com/browse/ACIP-536162*</a></p>

<p><b>Overview:</b> For In-store orders (Bakery and Deli service dept), associates can take the order using ACI tablets digital order form for long prep items.</p>

<p><b>Detailed requirements:</b> <a href="https://confluence.safeway.com/spaces/CDT/pages/597829096/Requirements+Areas+of+Work" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">https://confluence.safeway.com/spaces/CDT/pages/597829096/Requirements+Areas+of+Work</a></p>
<ul>
	<li><b>Service Dept</b> - Bakery and Deli</li>
	<li><b>Use Cases:</b> Ability for associates to take order digitally on tablet for: 1) Bakery Order 2) Bakery Catering Tray order 3) Deli Party Trays 4) Deli Holiday Meals</li>
	<li><b>Order Type</b> - In-Store MTO Order</li>
</ul>


<p><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b></p>

<p>1) Attributes</p>
<ul>
	<li>Support new attribute to support and enable in-store digital intake orders</li>
	<li>Might require additional attributes for capturing <ins>associate</ins> info as they will be taking this order for the customer,</li>
</ul>


<p>2) There will be NO payment when order is captured, so support orders without payment</p>

<p>3) Process these orders as in-store orders (NOT ecom orders, not follow ecommerce workflow)</p>

<p>5) No picker (AcuPick) integration. Order should go to DOMS.</p>

<p>6) No Slot integration</p>

<p>7) Associate can initiated Cancel Order for this cart but C&amp;C dont have to make any changes its out of scope to update status for the order </p>

<p>8) Cart category will be 1P_MTO_Kiosk </p>

<p>9) Pricing services is in scope (similar to Kiosk)</p>

<p>8) Associate can initiate Edit Order for this cart <b><font color="#de350b">(POST MLP)</font></b></p>

<p><font color="#4c9aff"><b>Added scope:</b> </font></p>

<p><font color="#4c9aff"><b>9) If the order for creative cake and custom tray it should not have price (as price is TBD)</b><br/>
<b>10) when cart just have TBD item dont show price</b> </font></p>

<p><font color="#4c9aff"><b>11) If the cart is mixed , fixed price item and creative cake or custom tray price will only be should for fixed price item creative cake or custom tray should show $0 .00 and est total should be $0.00</b></font></p>

<p><font color="#4c9aff"><b>12)</b> <b>Field should be added for message currently we have 2 feild for message going forward its should be 3</b></font></p>

<p><font color="#4c9aff"><b>-Decoration instruction</b> </font><br/>
<font color="#4c9aff"><b>-message /in</b></font><br/>
<font color="#4c9aff"><b>-additional message</b></font></p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

